Perfect solutions do not exist.
Do not assume anything -> what you know != what users know.
A way of moving forward is toquestion the status quo.
What is crucial to ask is 'who are we designing/creating for?'.

QQ Browser?
Cost control API on Firefox OS
Network link conditioner.

Understand the target group, its language, culture and ways of thinking while targeting an app.

Localization helps with reaching very foreign markets.
Even a small market share in China can mean several million users.